A very efficient and friendly service.My experience was wonderful, I recommend their  service.
thank you.
Quick solution and recommendation. A little late for the appointment but satisfied with the resolution
Doctor was very helpful and talked the way through the treatment and helped me navigate the issue i was facing.
Great calming environment and the musical background was therapeutic Dr Manoj was very cooperative and  friendly .

***** ** ** *********  ****** *** *** * ****** ***.  My full family are his patients. My husband has done his 2 implants with him and is very Happy. My son has filled his cavities and now is a regular patient with Manoj. He visits him religiously every 3 months and gets his dental cleaning done. I was the last person to visit him . But last and best is the treatment I got from him.  He solved my problem and gave me a painless tooth in minutes without using a needle.  He was referred to us by my neighbour Mrs Medha Nadkani. His reference was given to us by my old Dentist Dr Sonal Shetty.

Dr. Bodhwani is amazing in what he does. His friendly yet serious attitude is what makes him most reliable. His treatments are painless *** ********* *** he never fails to go that extra mile to ensure his patients health.

My case in particular was a rare case as this specific tooth had 3 roots instead of 1 being the general case. He identified and treated the same painlessly explaining me and keeping me in the loop throughout the process.

He has also helped in case of a dental emergency for my friend (whose tooth apparently cracked or something) in the middle of the night.

I went with a lot of complications - a couple of milk teeth chipping off (Yes, you head right! I have around 4 of them still and they are causing all round trouble), worn out old fillings, potential root canal treatment, tooth extraction and bridge...the works. 

I like how all the problems were thoroughly scrutinized and sorted to arrive at a logical treatment plan. I was kept in the loop at all times. Also, treatment was avoided, where not necessary. For example, where a tooth could be saved via filling with some trial and error as against doing a root canal. I don't know too many dentists who would do that as a root canal is always more expensive.

 I like the cheery, bright ambience of the clinic, too.

 I would highly recommend Dr. Manoj Bodhwani's clinic. It has reduced my deep fear of dental treatment considerably.

Highly Recommend you guys to go and visit him once before you take any decision. Manoj on Google and I visited him.
